    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "9c84fc8c_79288564",
        "filename": "buildbucket/appengine/model/utils.go",
        "patchSetId": 4
      },
      "lineNbr": 59,
      "author": {
        "id": 1003211
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-16T09:56:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Reading the function doc and the BuildID format spec, doesn\u0027t the upper bound need to have all 1s in the lower 20 bits? Although as it is you match the Python code...",
      "revId": "8759ed1f1d9ef24d764722d5215b36fb510c2efd",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "af4bae0d_adede346",
        "filename": "buildbucket/appengine/model/utils.go",
        "patchSetId": 4
      },
      "lineNbr": 59,
      "author": {
        "id": 1398165
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-17T01:12:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "No need to have all 1s in the lower 20bits. The logic is really complex and tricky which took me huge efforts to understand.\n\n\nThe build id is monotonically decreasing. The lowTime will generate highId and highTime will generate lowId. Meanwhile, we also need to make sure [lowTime, highTime) to [lowId, highId).\n\n\u003d\u003d\u003d\nLet’s say \nlowTime - 1h0min0ms.\nidTimeSegment(lowTime) -\u003e  id1:  0xFE0000 (the trailing four 0s are the lower 20 bits.)\n\nhighTime - 2h0min0ms\nidTimeSegment(highTime) -\u003e  id2:  0x8E0000\n\nIf we directly return [0x8E0000,  0xFE0000) which will lead to incorrect answer as user is unable to fetch those build ids 0xFE0000, 0xFE0011 etc..\nTherefore, we need to subtract 1ms from low and high time in IdRange function, so that \n\nidTimeSegment(lowTime.Add(-timeResolution)) -\u003e id1_1: 0xFF0000\nidTimeSegment(highTime.Add(-timeResolution)) -\u003e id2_1: 0x8F0000\n\nthen we get the correct range [0x8F0000, 0xFF0000).\n\u003d\u003d\u003d\n\nThose part are difficult so I also added more detailed comments in corresponding places.",
      "parentUuid": "9c84fc8c_79288564",
      "revId": "8759ed1f1d9ef24d764722d5215b36fb510c2efd",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
    },
